dct_description_sm: United States. Army Map Service Alternate title: Agadir. In upper left margin: Morocco 1:10,000. Lambert conical orthomorphic projection. N.W. Africa zone grid. Relief shown by form lines and spot elevation. "Prepared under the direction of the chief of engineers, U. S. Army ... Compiled from base map of Ville d'Agadir, 1:10,000, Office of the military attache, Tangier, Morocco. Revised from U. S. H. O. chart no. 2239, R. A. F. aerial photos ... and Morocco, town plan of Agadir, G. S. G. S. no. 4241, 1942."
dct_creator_sm: Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1942.
